de design inspired by whale fins improves turbine efficiency at moderate wind speeds without exceeding local noise limits.","is_correct":true,"explanation":"Correct (D). Logically necessary from the stated premises; requires no speculative leap beyond the text."}]'::jsonb, 'D', 'Step 1 — Identify what is stated
